msgid "Vertex groups only apply to Mesh and Lattice Objects."
msgstr "顶点组仅适用于网格和晶格物体."

#~ msgid "Any other Object type has no vertices, hence it cannot have Vertex Groups."
#~ msgstr "其他物体类型没有顶点，因此无法拥有顶点组。"

#~ msgid "Typical use cases for vertex groups."
#~ msgstr "顶点组的典型用例。"

#~ msgid "Skinning an Armature"
#~ msgstr "骨架蒙皮"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you want to animate your mesh and make it move, you will define an armature which consists "
#~ "of a bunch of bones. Vertex Groups are used to associate parts of the Mesh to Bones of the "
#~ "Armature, where you can specify an influence *weight* in the range (0.0 - 1.0) for each vertex "
#~ "in the Vertex Group."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "如果想驱动网格并且使它动起来，用户可以定义由一堆骨骼组成的骨架，用顶点组来将各个部分的网格与骨"
#~ "架中的骨骼联系起来，为每个顶点组里的顶点指定一个 (0.0 - 1.0) 范围内的支配 *权重*。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Obviously, the same vertex can belong to several groups, and hence be affected by several "
#~ "bones, with a fine tuning of each bone's influence using these vertex weights. Quite useful "
#~ "when you want to have a smooth joint. For example, when you skin an elbow, the upperarm vertex "
#~ "group contains the vertices of this part at full weight (*1.0*), and when reaching the elbow "
#~ "area, these weights decrease progressively to *0.0* when reaching the forearm zone and vice "
#~ "versa for the forearm group weights... Of course, this is a very raw example skinning a "
#~ "realistic joint is a big job, as you have to carefully find good weights for each vertex, to "
#~ "have the most realistic behavior, when bending -- and this is not an easy thing!"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "很明显，同一个顶点可以属于多个顶点组，因此可以受多个骨骼影响，使用顶点权重微调每个骨骼的影响。"
#~ "这有助于做出顺畅的关节。比如说当为肘关节蒙皮时，上臂顶点组包含的顶点为满权重 (*1.0*)，并且过了"
#~ "肘关切，到达前臂区域时，这些权重逐步地减小到 *0.0* ，前臂顶点组权重则是反过来的....当然，这是一"
#~ "个非常粗糙的例子，给一个真实的关节蒙皮是一个很大的任务，因为必须很仔细地为每个顶点找到合适的权"
#~ "重，这样才能实现在弯曲时最真实的动作 -- 这不是一件简单的事情！"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Many modifiers contain the ability to control the modifier influence on each vertex "
#~ "separately. This is also done via Vertex Groups and the weight values associated to the "
#~ "vertices."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "许多修改器包含单独控制对每个顶点的影响的能力。这个也是通过顶点组和与顶点关联的权重值实现的。"

