#~ msgstr "网格选择"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "By defining mesh regions with Vertex Groups you can easily select entire parts of your mesh "
#~ "with three clicks and work on them in isolation without having to create separate objects. "
#~ "With the Hide tool you can even remove a vertex group from the view (for later unhide)."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "通过顶点组定义网格区域，三次点击就可以轻易选择完整的网格区域，并且无需创建分离物体就可以独立地"
#~ "操作这些顶点。通过隐藏的功能，用户甚至可以从视图中移除一个顶点组(而后取消隐藏)。"
